title: Pink in the Rink event aims to raise money for patients in need (St Luke's ...
text: ( Source : St Luke's Hospital ) UnityPoint Health - St. Luke's Hospital and the Nassif Community Cancer Center is once again teaming up with the Cedar Rapids RoughRiders to help raise awareness of breast cancer with a Pink in the Rink event.
